snippet.title: Five CRPF Personnel Injured In Grenade Attack In Kashmir's Kulgam

localized.description:
Weeks after the terror strike on an Army Base in Uri where 18 soldiers were killed, a CRPF troop was attacked today in Anantnag district's Wan Poh in Jammu and Kashmir, where five jawans have been injured.
